  Description: 'Experience is the best teacher, is what they often say. Well, the
    coaches of the Wisconsin Sages have plenty of experience, and they really know
    how to train a young squad up to their max potential. This team is known for
    their strategic offense: Passing to find the best matchup, and juking to get
    inside and create the best shot they can. As a middle of the road unit the past
    few years, they are looking to turn things around  and bring home the championship
    for their fans.'
  CoachName: Bob Wedge
